B-Spline Regression examples

train_data <- data[1:2000,]

# weight
lm_age <- lm(wgt ~ age, train_data)
sb_age <- lm(wgt~bs(age, knots = c(8,14,16)), train_data)
lm_bs <- lm(wgt ~ factor(sex) + bs(age, knots = c(8,14,16)), train_data)


# prediction
data_new <- data[5001:6002,]


lm_pred <- predict(lm_age,data_new,interval = "prediction")

bs_pred <- predict(sb_age,data_new,interval = "prediction")

sb_sex <- predict(lm_bs,data_new,interval = "prediction")


data_new$lm <- lm_pred[,'fit']
data_new$sb_age <- bs_pred[,'fit']
data_new$lm_bs <- sb_sex[,'fit']


ggplot(data_new, aes(x=age, y=wgt)) + geom_point(color="green") +
  geom_line(aes(x=age,y=lm,color='Linear'),linetype = 2,size=1.5)+
  geom_line(aes(x=age,y=lm_bs,color='b_spline(age,sex)',),linetype = 2,size=1.5)+
  geom_line(aes(x=age,y=sb_age,color='b_spline(age)'),linetype = 1,size=1.5)+
  scale_color_manual(name='Regression Model',
                     breaks=c('Linear', 'b_spline(age)', 'b_spline(age,sex)'),
                     values=c('b_spline(age)'='blue', 'b_spline(age,sex)'='black', 'Linear'='red'))

# hight
lm_age <- lm(hgt ~ age, train_data)
sb_age <- lm(hgt~bs(age, knots = c(8,14,16)), train_data)

B-Spline Regression examples2 for wgt

lm_age <- lm(wgt ~ age, train_data)
sb_age <- lm(wgt~bs(age) , train_data)
lm_bs <- lm(wgt ~ factor(sex) + bs(age), train_data)


# prediction

lm_pred <- predict(lm_age,data_new,se=T)

bs_pred <- predict(sb_age,data_new,se=T)

sb_sex <- predict(lm_bs,data_new,se=T)

lm_pred <- data.frame(fit=lm_pred$fit,lwr=lm_pred$fit-2*lm_pred$se.fit,upr=lm_pred$fit+2*lm_pred$se.fit)
lm_pred$model <- rep('lm',nrow(lm_pred))


bs_pred <- data.frame(fit=bs_pred$fit,lwr=bs_pred$fit-2*bs_pred$se.fit,upr=bs_pred$fit+2*bs_pred$se.fit)
bs_pred$model <- rep('bs',nrow(bs_pred))


sb_sex <- data.frame(fit=sb_sex$fit,lwr=sb_sex$fit-2*sb_sex$se.fit,upr=sb_sex$fit+2*sb_sex$se.fit)
sb_sex$model <- paste(rep('bs_sex',nrow(sb_sex)),data_new$sex,sep = ":")
# sb_sex$model <- rep('bs_sex',nrow(sb_sex))



true_data <- data.frame(fit=data_new$wgt,
                        lwr=rep(0,nrow(data_new)),
                                upr=rep(0,nrow(data_new)),
                                model=rep("True",nrow(data_new)),
                        age=data_new$age
                        )


df <- rbind(lm_pred,bs_pred,sb_sex)
df$age <- rep(data_new$age,3)




ggplot(true_data,aes(x=age, y=fit)) + geom_point(colour="gray")+
  geom_line(data = df,aes(x=age,y=fit,colour=model),size=1.5)+ylab("wgt")

ggplot(data =df ,aes(x=age,y=fit,colour=model))+geom_line(size=1.5)+
  geom_ribbon(aes(ymin = lwr, ymax = upr), alpha = 0.1)+ylab("wgt")

plot_pred <- function(col){
  
  df1 <- df[df$model %in% c(col),]
  
  ggplot(true_data,aes(x=age, y=fit)) + geom_point(colour="gray")+
    geom_line(data = df1,aes(x=age,y=fit,color="pred"),linetype = 1,size=1.5)+
    geom_line(data = df1,aes(x=age,y=lwr,color='lower'),linetype = 2,size=1)+
    geom_line(data = df1,aes(x=age,y=upr,color='upper'),linetype = 2,size=1)+
    scale_color_manual(name=col,
                     breaks=c('pred', 'lower', 'upper'),
                     values=c('pred'='red', 'lower'='blue', 'upper'='blue'))+ylab("wgt")

  
}


plot_pred('lm')

plot_pred('bs')

plot_pred('bs_sex:boy')

plot_pred('bs_sex:girl')
